name: Lydia Nashly
description:
I am a very sociable person. My friends say I am very kind girl and I believe them. I have good sense of humor. I always try to keep myself in a good mood. I am soft, tender and passionate girl with a big wish to love!
I am looking for a man who is family-oriented, faithful, honest and strong. I want to trust him, I want to support him. His age, nationality doesn’t matter for me if he is my man. I want to communicate with him.
